title: The Ultimate Matchmaker
overview: The Ultimate Matchmaker follows the staff of a select dating agency in London where the clientele seemingly have it all - except "The One".Help is on hand in the form of dating expert and matchmaker to the elite Lara Asprey, a woman who knows exactly what her super eligible clients are looking for - and how to make the perfect match. As we get to know Lara, her extraordinary team and all the affluent singletons looking for love, The Ultimate Matchmaker gives W viewers a unique insight into the glamorous world of high class dating.
